Download the original plink file data set provided on https://alkesgroup.broadinstitute.org/LDSCORE/GRCh38/plink_files.tgz
Untar the file use command tar zxvf plink_files.tgz
Download and install plink 1.9 from https://www.cog-genomics.org/plink/ or from Anaconda;
Copy the associated make_merged_plink_set.sh file into the untared plink_files folder;
Execute bash make_merged_plink_set.sh
